Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子  呃\N{\fs12}Son, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能留在这\N{\fs12}l want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我坚持这么久的主要原因\N{\fs12}That's the main reason l've stuck around for so damn long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  尼克  请进\N{\fs12}Hey, Nick. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我接替你工作六周吗\N{\fs12}You want me to cover for you for six weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你知道的  我要开始休产假了\N{\fs12}Yeah, you know, just for my maternity leave.
