Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  阿尔文  如果你觉得做不了的话\N{\fs12}You know, Alvin, if you don't think that you're up to it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去找别人来给我替班\N{\fs12}then l can find someone else to cover for me.\N{\fs12}你知道的  阿尔文  如果你觉得做不了的话\N{\fs12}You know, Alvin, if you don't think that you're up to it
