Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呢\N{\fs12}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我也不知道  但是\N{\fs12}Well, l don't know, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以的  露露  真的\N{\fs12}l'm up to it, Lulu, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fs12}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  尼克  - 阿尔文\N{\fs12}- Hey, Nick. - Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  能跟你说两句吗\N{\fs12}Lulu, do you have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我刚刚见我的缓刑监察员  - 是嘛\N{\fs12}- l just saw my probation omicer. - Okay.
