Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再有17小时  我就做完了\N{\fs12}17 hours and l'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  很好啊\N{\fs12}Hmm. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  呃\N{\fs12}Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  你说有没做完的案子都要转交给其他律师的\N{\fs12}You know, all of your open cases will have to be transferred to other attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我给你的缓刑监察官准备文书\N{\fs12}And l'll start the paperwork for your probation officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Great. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说没有  这个  凯文  凯文·布朗\N{\fs12}You know what? Here. Kevin. Kevin·Brown.
