Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  欢迎来到刑事法庭\N{\fs12}Well, welcome to the criminal courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗\N{\fs12}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩怀孕了  并且两周之前生下了孩子\N{\fs12}The girl was impregnated, and she had the baby two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想把她送给别人领养\N{\fs12}Wants to give her up for adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是凯文不想放弃他作为父亲的权利  所以\N{\fs12}The problem is that Kevin doesn't want to relinquish his parental rights, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这个只会花八个小时  那你有其他的\N{\fs12}Right. Well, this'll only take eight hours, so do you have another?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  当然\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给  拿着这个吧\N{\fs12}Here, take that.
