Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他上诉失败了  他们会处死他\N{\fs12}He loses the appeal, they're gonna execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么我能帮忙的吗\N{\fs12}Can l help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我来见凯文·布朗\N{\fs12}l'm here to see Kevin·Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没有强奸她  - 我不是公共辩护人  凯文\N{\fs12}- l didn't rape her. - l'm not a public defender, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我这三年都没有犯罪\N{\fs12}Yo, l haven't committed a crime in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加了补习班  在学校的成绩都是A和B\N{\fs12}l joined the leg-up program and was gettin' all A's and B's in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文  凯文\N{\fs12}Kevin. Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道法庭正在考虑的是\N{\fs12}Do you understand that the court is considering
