Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能这样做\N{\fs12}They can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果你最后坐牢了  他们就有权利这样\N{\fs12}Well, they can if you end up in prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或者如果法官相信孩子妈妈的话\N{\fs12}or if the judge believes the mother of your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  这都是些废话\N{\fs12}l mean, that's some crap right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是废话  你有两次前科\N{\fs12}lt's not crap. You have two prior convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一次是吸毒  另一次是袭击他人\N{\fs12}One for drugs and another for assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我没有强奸她\N{\fs12}But l didn't rape her.
