Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且备选家庭都是不错的\N{\fs12}And the potential family's an excellent placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没有强奸她  - 我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}- l didn't rape her. - l get it. l get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她之前是我的女朋友\N{\fs12}She was my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她之前是的\N{\fs12}She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她也是很喜欢我的\N{\fs12}Like, she was real interested in me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我改变了我的生活和所有的一切\N{\fs12}for the way l changed my life around and whatever.
