Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,塔利克\N{\fs12}Taliek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文·马斯特森\N{\fs12}Alvin·Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这是因为我知道你解雇了你最好的律师\N{\fs12}l'm here because l understand you fired your Iatest attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  克里斯  你的档案写着你一直呆在自己的牢房里\N{\fs12}So, Chris, your file says you wouldn't come out of your cell?
