Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果你不加入到白人孩子的阵营  他们基本会把你当黑人孩子对待\N{\fs12}And if you don't join the white kids, they basically treat you like a black kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  这里的精神病医生  克里斯  他们并没有把你归类成精神病\N{\fs12}Well, the psychiatrists here, Chris, are not classifying you as mentally ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不能一直呆在这\N{\fs12}So you can't stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也不用回到曼科了  是吧\N{\fs12}But l don't have to go back to Manko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这得由法官来定\N{\fs12}That'll be up to the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以把我送去寄养家庭什么的\N{\fs12}Well, maybe you could put me in a foster family or something?\N{\fs12}这得由法官来定\N{\fs12}That'll be up to the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以把我送去寄养家庭什么的\N{\fs12}Well, maybe you could put me in a foster family or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我试试看可不可以\N{\fs12}Well, l'll see what l can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我真的不能再回曼科了\N{\fs12}l can't go back to Manko, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  终止我委托人父母权利的动议\N{\fs12}Your Honor, the motion to terminate my client's parental rights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还是为时过早的\N{\fs12}is completely premature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  他的当事人因强奸罪被捕\N{\fs12}His client was arrested for rape, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文·布朗还没有被定罪\N{\fs12}Kevin·Brown has not been convicted of any crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一项指控\N{\fs12}There's only been an accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个相当严重的指控\N{\fs12}Quite a serious accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但也只是一项指控\N{\fs12}But it's only an accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而也这也不是你当事人第一次\N{\fs12}And it's not the first time your client--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他在刑事审判中被判无罪\N{\fs12}lf he's found not guilty in his criminal trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他就应该有跟孩子保持关系的机会\N{\fs12}then he should be given the opportunity to have a relationship with his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,刑事定罪并不是必须的\N{\fs12}A criminal conviction is not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为法院有权终止凯文·布朗的权利\N{\fs12}for this court to terminate Kevin·Brown's rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  富勒夫妇是一个模范家庭\N{\fs12}Your Honor, the Fullers have identified an exemplary family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也准备好领养\N{\fs12}who are ready to adopt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人的孩子是应该被带走的\N{\fs12}No one should have their child taken away from them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅因为他们被指控犯罪\N{\fs12}simply because they've been accused of a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道找一个家庭有多困难吗\N{\fs12}Do you understand how dimicult it is to find families
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能愿意收养强奸怀孕后出生的孩子\N{\fs12}to adopt children conceived in rape?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保留裁决  一两天后给出最后决定\N{\fs12}l'll reserve judgment. You'll get my decision in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,曼科中心的环境太差了  导致我的当事人\N{\fs12}The conditions at the Manko Center are so bad that my client
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,精神崩溃  并且被送到了精神病医院\N{\fs12}had a mental breakdown and was institutionalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有发现患上精神疾病\N{\fs12}And found not to be mentally ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他不从自己的牢房出来  不吃  也不洗澡\N{\fs12}He doesn't come out of his cell. He doesn't eat. He doesn't shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,据医生所说  这些行为是他自己想做的  而不是由于疾\N{\fs12}According to the doctors, those behaviors are his choice, not an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  曼科中心应该是一个拘留所  而不是监狱\N{\fs12}Well, the Manko Center is supposed to be are formatory, not a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为拉普先生袭击一名八岁的女孩  我判他去训练营\N{\fs12}l sentenced Mr. Rapp to boot camp for assaulting an eight-year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,之后他袭击了一名社会工作者\N{\fs12}He then attacked a social worker
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一个尝试帮他从那转出来的人\N{\fs12}who was trying to help get him transferred from that very camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  但是事实是\N{\fs12}But the fact remains, Your Honor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,曼科中心并没有是我的当事人恢复正常生活\N{\fs12}that the Manko Center is not rehabilitating my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  事实是\N{\fs12}The fact remains, Mr. Fallin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,曼科中心是给最糟糕的情况预留的\N{\fs12}that the Manko Center is reserved for the worst of the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果让我说  他就只配待在那里\N{\fs12}lf you ask me, he's more than earned his place there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  嘿  很抱歉我迟到了  - 没事\N{\fs12}- Oh, hey. Sorry l'm late. - That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我能喝杯伏特加吗  你要来杯可乐还是别的什么\N{\fs12}Uh, can l have a vodka-tonic? You want a Coke or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不要了\N{\fs12}No, l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  有什么事吗\N{\fs12}So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下吃点吗\N{\fs12}You want to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我吃过了\N{\fs12}No, l already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坐下聊  好吗\N{\fs12}Let's sit down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想过你会想把我赶出公司\N{\fs12}l had no idea you wanted me out of the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我只是在做我认为能让公司未来更好的事\N{\fs12}Well, l'm just doing what l feel is best for the future of the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果有人问我  我会告诉他们你是一个一流的律师\N{\fs12}And if anyone asks me, l will tell them that you are a top-notch lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们你能带来客户  告诉他们你很有才华\N{\fs12}that you bring in clients and that you are talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在你应该离开\N{\fs12}But it's time for you to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从我自己的公司离开吗\N{\fs12}From my own firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧   看到没有  这就是问题的所在\N{\fs12}Well, see that's where the problem rests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我和希金斯，马斯顿和斯通\N{\fs12}because me and Higgins and Marston and Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来的时间都比你长\N{\fs12}have all been there Ionger than you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们付出的比你多  我们也有比你更多的客户\N{\fs12}We bill more than you do. We have more clients than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说  我们很不喜欢你的名字出现在门上\N{\fs12}And frankly, we're tired of having your name on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是说  在我们看来  法林&法林\N{\fs12}l mean, the way we see it, Fallin & Fallin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其实应是法林&希金斯&马斯特森&斯通\N{\fs12}is really Fallin & Higgins & Marston & Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&斯特拉卡\N{\fs12}& Straka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&法林\N{\fs12}& Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你插队了\N{\fs12}But you jumped the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你不可能将这件事情私人化\N{\fs12}Look, l know there's no way that you can't take this personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不应该\N{\fs12}but you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺喜欢你的  尼克  是真的挺喜欢\N{\fs12}l like you Nick. l really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉事情发展到这一步\N{\fs12}l'm sorry it had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  杰克那边怎么样了\N{\fs12}So how'd it go with Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为周四那群家伙有谁会改变阵营\N{\fs12}l don't think any of those guys are gonna change their position by Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  多赛特现在支持我们了\N{\fs12}Well, Doucette's with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  那你答应给她什么了\N{\fs12}Great. What'd you have to give her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 青石  - 多少\N{\fs12}- Bluestone. - How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,全部\N{\fs12}All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  明天我要和比尔·戈登开个早餐会\N{\fs12}Well, tomorrow l have a breakfast meeting with Bill·Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我明天晚餐的时候和兰德斯堡约一下\N{\fs12}Well, l'll set up, uh, some kinda dinner thing with Landsburg tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  周四我也会做完所有社区服务\N{\fs12}Oh, l'll be finishing my community service on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能做完吗\N{\fs12}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,缓刑基本结束了\N{\fs12}Probation's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  XX\N{\fs12}Well, you're working full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,斯特拉卡没法跟你比\N{\fs12}Straka can't compete with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能\N{\fs12}He can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,法官不打算给我机会了  是吗\N{\fs12}This judge isn't gonna give me a chance, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我想她不会给了\N{\fs12}No, l don't think she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她把孩子带走  我就不可能再看见她了  是吗\N{\fs12}lf she takes the baby away, l won't have any way to see her again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我看看孩子吗  五分钟就行\N{\fs12}Think l could get five minutes with the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧  如果在法官裁决之前你主动同意终止你的权利\N{\fs12}Maybe. If you agree to relinquish your rights before the judge rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也许能做一些什么\N{\fs12}l may be able to work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有见到过她  法林先生  我就是想看看她\N{\fs12}l've never seen her, Mr. Fallin. l just want to see her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了  我很抱歉  我真的不能待在这\N{\fs12}Please. l'm sorry. l just can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 他不出来上课\N{\fs12}- What's going on? - He won't come out for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我跟他谈谈吧  我是他的律师\N{\fs12}Let me talk to him. l'm his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我同意你跟他说几句话  你愿意出来吗\N{\fs12}lf l let you talk to this guy, you'll come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三分钟\N{\fs12}Three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我昨晚听到他们说话了  - 谁\N{\fs12}- l heard them last night. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那些黑人孩子\N{\fs12}The black kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到他们中有一个人说他要揍我\N{\fs12}l heard one of them say he was gonna stick me.
