Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们在哪  - 我不知道  是在熄灯之后\N{\fs12}- Where were they? - l don't know. It was after lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我听到了  先生  - 好的\N{\fs12}- l heard 'em, man. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们会做什么吗\N{\fs12}You know what they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会戳你的腋窝  这样你的肺就会被刺穿\N{\fs12}They stab you in the armpit so your lung gets punctured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯  这里有安保的  这些人会保护你的\N{\fs12}Chris, there's security here. There's people here to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你在说什么\N{\fs12}You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有三个月了  当你满18周岁了  你就能从这出去\N{\fs12}You got three months to go. When you're 18, you're out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就按照规矩  去学校  老实一点\N{\fs12}Just play by the rules. Go to school and keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为这样就可以了吗\N{\fs12}You really think that'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太张扬  好吗\N{\fs12}Just keep to yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你需要的修订本\N{\fs12}Here's the revised copies you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  好的  谢谢\N{\fs12}Yeah, okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  尼克  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey, Nick. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在比尔·戈登也在我们这边了\N{\fs12}So Bill·Gordon's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,需要给他豪斯特勒煤炭公司的一半  但是他还是加入我们的阵营了\N{\fs12}Had to give him half of Hostetler Coal, but he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟兰德博格聊过了吗\N{\fs12}Did you talk to Landsburg already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为他已经做好决定了\N{\fs12}l don't think he's made his mind up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,斯特拉卡他昨晚订婚了\N{\fs12}Straka. He got engaged last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟凯特·肖吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- To Kate Shaw? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一步好棋  老人有很多钱  也有很好的关系\N{\fs12}That's a good move. Old man's got a lot of money, good connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一步好棋\N{\fs12}lt's a good move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好去说一句祝贺\N{\fs12}l'd better go say congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯强烈反对死刑\N{\fs12}James was against the death penalty, vehemently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他会反对塔利克·艾伦的判刑\N{\fs12}And l know he would be opposed to what is about to happen to Taliek·Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在处理塔利克的上诉\N{\fs12}l am handling Taliek's appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们能给我一份宣誓书  那就帮了大忙了\N{\fs12}lt would help me a great deal if l could get an affidavit from you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,声明你们知道詹姆斯对死刑的看法\N{\fs12}stating that you knew James' view on capital punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你们支持判塔利克无期徒刑  而不是死刑\N{\fs12}and that you support a life sentence for Taliek instead of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是一个艰难的时刻\N{\fs12}l know this is a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,并不会\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看到他们把我弟弟詹姆斯按倒在地上的时候\N{\fs12}When l watched them lower my brother James into the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是艰难的时刻\N{\fs12}that was a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  知道塔利克·艾伦会像狗一样被杀掉\N{\fs12}Today, knowing that Taliek·Allen will be put down like the dog he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一段轻松的时刻  马斯特森先生\N{\fs12}that's a very easy time, Mr. Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯不会希望这样的\N{\fs12}James wouldn't want it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟还希望能活着呢\N{\fs12}My brother would've wanted to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你想道歉  否则不要再给我们打电话了\N{\fs12}Don't call on us again unless you plan to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安琪拉\N{\fs12}Angela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我请见詹姆斯的家人来见了一面  - 为什么啊\N{\fs12}- l asked James' family to meet with me. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为了签署宣誓书\N{\fs12}To sign an affidavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表塔利克·艾伦上诉\N{\fs12}l'm representing Taliek·Allen in his appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候  - 昨天\N{\fs12}- Since when? - Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不反对死刑吗\N{\fs12}You're not opposed to the death penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我反对啊  我对这个也有意见\N{\fs12}l'm opposed. l have my issues with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你要不要考虑签署一下宣誓书\N{\fs12}Well, would you consider signing an amidavit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,说你知道詹姆斯也是反对的\N{\fs12}stating that you knew James was against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我签署\N{\fs12}You want me to sign something stating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道詹姆斯反对死刑的宣誓书吗\N{\fs12}that l knew James was against the death penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 他真的反对吗\N{\fs12}- Yes. - Was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然反对的\N{\fs12}Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,并不知道\N{\fs12}Didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  瓦奥莱特\N{\fs12}Hi, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候到的\N{\fs12}When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs12}l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这等一下  好吗\N{\fs12}You wait right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我需要你接手我的一个客户\N{\fs12}Alvin, l need you to take over one of my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我现在很忙\N{\fs12}No, l'm very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字叫瓦奥莱特·桑兹  她的养父母将搬到内华达州\N{\fs12}Her name is Violet·Sands. Her foster parents are moving to Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要一个好的寄宿家庭\N{\fs12}She needs a good placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不能管她\N{\fs12}Why can't you take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在周末之前做完\N{\fs12}l'm gonna be done by the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做完什么  - 做完这个\N{\fs12}- Done with what? - Done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做完这吗  - 我还剩11小时\N{\fs12}- Done here? - l got 1 1 hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦奥莱特  这是阿尔文·马斯特森\N{\fs12}Violet, this is Alvin·Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始  由阿尔文来照顾你\N{\fs12}Alvin will be taking care of you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你听说杰克和凯特的事了吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Did you hear about Jake and Kate? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我该怎么做了\N{\fs12}l don't know what l'm gonna do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  她是我的好朋友之一\N{\fs12}l mean, she's one of my really good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为她不了解杰克吗\N{\fs12}You don't think she knows about Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  她同意嫁给他  所以  不  我觉得她不知道\N{\fs12}Well, she agreed to marry him. So no, l don't think she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该告诉她  你不觉得吗\N{\fs12}l have to tell her, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算跟她说什么\N{\fs12}What are you gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我不知道  可能说他以前跟男人睡过\N{\fs12}Um, l don't know. That he's been with men, l guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你吧\N{\fs12}lt's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不关系你的尼克都做了什么\N{\fs12}l don't care what you say Nick did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你把尼克投出去了  你也把我投出去了\N{\fs12}You vote Nick out, you vote me out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fs12}ls that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你要结婚了\N{\fs12}l heard you're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜  凯特很不错\N{\fs12}Congratulations. Kate's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的有很多转变\N{\fs12}That's a lot of changes happening for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,新的未婚妻  新的客户  新的衣服\N{\fs12}New fiancée. New clients. New clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你知道  我觉得我们也许应该一起坐下来\N{\fs12}Well, you know, l was thinking maybe we could sit down together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后敲定一下新的薪酬结构\N{\fs12}and hammer out a new pay structure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,基于计费工时  和源信贷合作\N{\fs12}based on billable hours, working with source credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚谁能从每个客户那里得到什么  而不是把整个公司搞得四分五裂\N{\fs12}Figure out who gets what of each client instead of tearing this entire firm apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在威胁我吗\N{\fs12}Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么说\N{\fs12}Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你问什么要提到凯特\N{\fs12}Why would you bring up Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  我是在祝贺你们的好消息\N{\fs12}Jake, l was congratulating you\N{\fs12}on your good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我们可以找一份客户名单  单独坐下来\N{\fs12}So, we can get a client list, we can sit down together, alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后试着安排好一切\N{\fs12}and try to come to some kind of an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  但是你为什么要把凯特卷进来\N{\fs12}Yeah, but why would you bring Kate into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有  杰克\N{\fs12}l'm not, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我想跟凯特说你的事情  我早就说了\N{\fs12}lf l wanted to tell Kate about you, l would've done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是在威胁我\N{\fs12}You're threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直信守对你的承诺  没告诉别人\N{\fs12}l've kept my promises to you. l've covered for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有说过关于你的情况\N{\fs12}l've kept quiet about your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我想我现在有点好奇  你为什么现在要这样想我\N{\fs12}So l guess l'm a little curious as to why you would be doing this to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在威胁我\N{\fs12}You're threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈明天晚上想邀请你的妈妈来吃饭\N{\fs12}My mom wants to invite your mom over for dinner tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我妈妈已经雇了一个非常棒的婚礼策划师\N{\fs12}Oh, my mother has hired this insane wedding planner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸说他要在威廉佩·恩酒店订三层楼\N{\fs12}And my dad thought he might reserve three floors at the William·Penn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼的周末\N{\fs12}the weekend of the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,凯特  你还记不记得  呃\N{\fs12}Kate, do you remember, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得我被抢劫的时候吗\N{\fs12}Do you remember when l was mugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,记得\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  其实不只是  那样\N{\fs12}Well, it wasn't just... that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我 被  呃\N{\fs12}l was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我被性侵了\N{\fs12}l was attacked... sexually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人  他  呃\N{\fs12}The man, he, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他袭击了我\N{\fs12}Well, he attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前为什么不告诉我\N{\fs12}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我觉得很丢人\N{\fs12}l--l was ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃\N{\fs12}l, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你可能会觉得我太弱了\N{\fs12}l guess l thought you might think that l was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他强奸了你吗\N{\fs12}He raped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有些人  呃\N{\fs12}And now some people are, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  他们  他们在  呃\N{\fs12}well, they're--they're, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,散布谣言  说我\N{\fs12}spreading rumors that l'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想跟我说什么\N{\fs12}What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望这一切都能过去\N{\fs12}l just want to get past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是  我想我能理解\N{\fs12}What l'm saying is l guess l understand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果因为这个让你不想跟我在一起\N{\fs12}if this makes you not want to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  我爱你\N{\fs12}Jake, l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该更早告诉你的\N{\fs12}l should've told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  如果你需要一些时间来考虑这件事  我能理解的\N{\fs12}Look, l just understand if you need some time to think about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:22:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有效的法律顾问协助  这才是我们的论点\N{\fs12}lneffective assistance of counsel. That's our argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这里没有\N{\fs12}See here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fs12}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fs12}here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你证明了你对詹姆斯有很强烈的愤怒\N{\fs12}You testified about the intense rage you felt towards James
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的攻击造成了你的毁容\N{\fs12}because his attack caused your disfigurement,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你失去了自己的孩子\N{\fs12}because you lost your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你的律师从来不为极端的情绪做辩护\N{\fs12}Well, your lawyer never argued extreme emotional disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你可能不会得到正面的直接辩护\N{\fs12}Affirmative defenses that probably couldn't have gotten you off,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但他本可以将刑期减为无期徒刑  而不是  呃\N{\fs12}but could have mitigated the sentence to life instead of, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  而不是其他刑罚\N{\fs12}well, instead of the alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要跟孩子相处多长时间\N{\fs12}How long does he want to spend with the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟  就是亲自看看她\N{\fs12}A few minutes. Just to see her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们同意  凯文会选择终止他作为父母的权利\N{\fs12}lf you agree, Kevin will relinquish his parental rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我觉得没什么不好的\N{\fs12}Well, l don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是可以的吗\N{\fs12}So it's agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先说明  我需要先跟我妻子说说  但是我并不觉得有什么不好的\N{\fs12}l mean, l have to talk to my wife first, but l don't think there'll be a problem.
