Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在这待着有多糟糕  - 你想说什么\N{\fs12}- How bad is it in here? - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你们这一个孩子的律师\N{\fs12}l represent this kid in your unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他害怕到从来不从牢房出来\N{\fs12}He so frightened he never comes out of his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  那个白胖子吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- What, that fat white kid? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他自作自受  他太紧张了  总是逼着自己那样想\N{\fs12}He got it bad. He's too nervous. Calls attention to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他说要想在这里生存下去  就得加入一边\N{\fs12}But he says to survive in this place you gotta join a gang.
