Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你必须要通过XX来抢一个自己的位置\N{\fs12}Yeah, you gotta earn your place by jumpin' somebody, drawing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们之后再联系  - 好的\N{\fs12}- l'll be in touch. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直低头做人  法林先生\N{\fs12}l kept my head down, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你说的一样\N{\fs12}Just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很低调\N{\fs12}l kept my head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯先生格拉斯太太  我需要知道\N{\fs12}l need to know the minute Mr. and Mrs. Glass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快定下来  好吗\N{\fs12}come to a decision, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  尼克  - 嘿  最近怎么样\N{\fs12}- Hey, Nick. - Hey, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这几天太忙了\N{\fs12}lt's been a wild couple a days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是  恭喜\N{\fs12}l bet. Well, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看到凯特了\N{\fs12}l just saw Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.30,0:24:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是的  她  呃\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah. She, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她过来  想要聊聊杰克的事情\N{\fs12}She came by and she wanted to talk about Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他可能跟她说了那次袭击的事  她有点吓坏了\N{\fs12}l guess he told her about the attack. She was kinda freaked out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么了吗\N{\fs12}Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.96,0:24:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我也不能  我只是\N{\fs12}No. l couldn't. l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.94,0:24:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我转了话题  跟她聊了聊婚礼派对的事\N{\fs12}l just changed the subject and talked about her wedding shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗  - 还好\N{\fs12}- You okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,凯特跟我说你和杰克在工作中有些问题\N{\fs12}Kate told me that you and Jake were having some problems at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.16,0:24:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.59,0:24:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  现在怎么样了\N{\fs12}Well, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克想把我从我的公司中赶出去\N{\fs12}Jake's trying to get me thrown out of my firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  你怎么没有跟我说\N{\fs12}What? Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你不需要有压力的  你马上就要生了\N{\fs12}Oh, you don't need the stress. You're about to have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我希望你不要觉得尴尬\N{\fs12}Well, l hope you're not embarrassed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  一点也不会\N{\fs12}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.16,0:25:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我并不在意你是否在那家公司工作\N{\fs12}Because l don't care if you work for that firm or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我还是很在意的\N{\fs12}Well, l kinda do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.66,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.88,0:25:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有几个小时了\N{\fs12}How many hours do you have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.42,0:25:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,四个\N{\fs12}Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马上就结束了  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- End of an era. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,终于要结束了\N{\fs12}End of an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.06,0:25:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这支笔\N{\fs12}This pen...
