Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.90,0:25:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这支笔是我爸爸高中毕业的时候收到的\N{\fs12}This pen was given to my father for his high school graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爷爷给的\N{\fs12}by my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.94,0:25:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是1954年的XX  金尖\N{\fs12}lt's a 1954 Alt-Rodere, gold-tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,花了我爷爷一周的薪水\N{\fs12}lt cost my grandfather a week's salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.74,0:25:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我想把它给你  尼克\N{\fs12}l want you to have it, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.99,0:25:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你什么都不用给我的\N{\fs12}Alvin, you don't have to give me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.04,0:25:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你记得在这的时光\N{\fs12}To remember your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.34,0:25:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你得承认  你是挺喜欢在这工作的\N{\fs12}You gotta admit, you kinda liked working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  呃  我可没有\N{\fs12}Nope. No. l, uh... l didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.24,0:26:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  非常犯些\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.78,0:26:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  这是达姆森法官办公室给你的\N{\fs12}Nick, this just came from Judge Damsen's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢\N{\fs12}Great. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.38,0:26:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道  - 你这道这意味着什么吗\N{\fs12}- l knew it. - You understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,根据法官所说的  我再也不是我孩子的爸爸了\N{\fs12}That l'm not my baby's daddy anymore,\N{\fs12}according to this judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯夫妇改变了对于你看孩子的想法\N{\fs12}The Glasses have changed their mind about your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.60,0:26:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯太太有点担心\N{\fs12}Mrs. Glass is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,担心什么  她害怕我吗\N{\fs12}Concerned? What, she scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她相信了你的事情\N{\fs12}She believes the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有  先生  我真的没有强奸那个女生\N{\fs12}l have never-- Man, l did not rape that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  她相信了那个女孩的事\N{\fs12}Well, she believes the girl's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.16,0:26:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是他已经答应我了  先生  - 很抱歉\N{\fs12}- But he promised me, man! - l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.48,0:26:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不行  你听到了的  他已经答应我了\N{\fs12}No, man! He promised me! You heard him promise me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.86,0:27:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯  你感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}Chris, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.56,0:27:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是谢谢你了  混蛋  他们快杀了我了\N{\fs12}Thanks a lot, jerk-om. They're gonna kill me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.94,0:27:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊\N{\fs12}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.36,0:27:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟卡拉克森主管说了我的事情吗\N{\fs12}You told Director Clarkson what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.18,0:27:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我当然说了\N{\fs12}Yeah, of course l did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.70,0:27:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他去找那个打我的家伙了\N{\fs12}He went after the kid that did this to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.86,0:27:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他的同伙要杀了吧  除非我做些什么\N{\fs12}and now his buddies are gonna kill me... unless l can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该把我弄出去\N{\fs12}You should have got me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是把时间都花在那个黑小子身上\N{\fs12}lnstead of spending all your time with that black kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该来帮我的\N{\fs12}you should have been helping me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第六修正案保证了所有人\N{\fs12}The Sixth Amendment guarantees all persons
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.84,0:27:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在辩护时能得到律师的协助\N{\fs12}assistance of counsel for their defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.50,0:27:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,法院也一再解释这是适当的\N{\fs12}lt has been repeatedly interpreted by the courts to mean adequate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.32,0:27:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,并且熟练的法律顾问\N{\fs12}and skilled counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.46,0:27:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我在法庭上努力阐明的\N{\fs12}As l have made it painfully clear to this court,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.60,0:27:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,塔利克·艾路从来没有这样的代表\N{\fs12}Taliek·Allen was never amorded such representation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.28,0:27:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,英联邦想要剥夺塔利克·艾伦的生命\N{\fs12}The Commonwealth wants to take Taliek·Allen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.82,0:28:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他被判处死刑\N{\fs12}He has been condemned to die
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.94,0:28:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我们宪法的规定\N{\fs12}despite the fact that the rules of our Constitution
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.60,0:28:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有被遵守\N{\fs12}have not been adhered to,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这很明显是不公平的\N{\fs12}and that is an irreversible injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.76,0:28:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡不是随便就能发给谁的东西\N{\fs12}Death is not something to be handed out arbitrarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.18,0:28:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我们之前已经达成一致\N{\fs12}An agreement was reached, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.28,0:28:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这不在我们的考虑范围内\N{\fs12}For which there was no consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.94,0:28:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的当事人愿意签署终止协议\N{\fs12}My client was willing to sign the termination papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还不够吗\N{\fs12}ls that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.34,0:28:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这项协议是建立在假设的基础上的\N{\fs12}The agreement was based on the presumption
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的签名才是必须的\N{\fs12}his signature would be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.08,0:28:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止  协议不能强制执行\N{\fs12}lt isn't any longer. The agreement isn't enforceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.70,0:28:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯先生  请听我说完  我需要再跟你谈谈\N{\fs12}Mr. Glass, if you'd just hear me out. l need to talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.92,0:28:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  你的父亲在最高法院辩护过对吧\N{\fs12}Nick, your father's argued before the Supreme Court, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.32,0:28:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 你那个时候帮他处理案子了吗\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - Did you help him with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.02,0:28:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,参与了一点吧  怎么了\N{\fs12}A little. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我起草了调卷领  也许你可以看看\N{\fs12}l drafted a Writ of Certiorari. Maybe you could take a look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.40,0:28:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你要上诉到最高法院吗\N{\fs12}You're gonna appeal to the Supreme Court?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.22,0:28:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能就这样看着他死  尼克\N{\fs12}l can't just let him die, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.28,0:29:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.00,0:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.62,0:29:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,躲起来\N{\fs12}Hiding.
