Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.34,0:29:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他\N{\fs12}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢他\N{\fs12}l don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  露露\N{\fs12}Well-- Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.30,0:29:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来一下\N{\fs12}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.58,0:29:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是露露  先让她照顾你一会  好吗\N{\fs12}This is Lulu. She's gonna take care of you just for a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就一会\N{\fs12}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.14,0:29:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,法律顾问的协助吗\N{\fs12}lnemective assistance of counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.06,0:29:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,值得一试\N{\fs12}lt's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.50,0:29:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到底怎么回事  - 什么意思\N{\fs12}- What's this about? - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.52,0:29:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道到底怎么回事\N{\fs12}No, what is this really about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.04,0:29:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,死刑是野蛮的\N{\fs12}The death penalty's barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.58,0:29:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我并不认为只是关于死刑的问题\N{\fs12}l don't think it's about the death penalty, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:30:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  你觉得是跟我自己有关吗  不是的\N{\fs12}What, you think this is about me? It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上是塔利克·艾伦不应该死\N{\fs12}lt's about the fact that Taliek·Allen does not deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.52,0:30:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有活着的权利\N{\fs12}Everyone has a right to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.68,0:30:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  真的不是我自己的原因\N{\fs12}Well, it's not about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.08,0:30:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉给你打了好多次电话\N{\fs12}l'm sorry l called you so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.44,0:30:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没关系的  - 我不确定我还能跟谁说\N{\fs12}- It's all right. - l wasn't sure who else to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.76,0:30:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这件事  露露有点奇怪  所以我猜想我们可以聊聊\N{\fs12}Lulu was being weird about it, and l guess l thought we could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.72,0:30:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.88,0:30:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你和杰克现在有些矛盾\N{\fs12}l know that you and Jake are having some problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.36,0:30:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得你是最了解他的人\N{\fs12}but l thought, well, you're the person who knows him the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.62,0:30:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  可能我不应该这样说\N{\fs12}Well, l wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.64,0:30:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是杰克之前一直在夸你\N{\fs12}Jake always spoke so highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.98,0:30:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  很高兴听到这个\N{\fs12}Well, that's nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  现在变了\N{\fs12}Now that's... changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.06,0:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克变了很多\N{\fs12}Jake's kind of changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.98,0:30:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我说了那次袭击\N{\fs12}He told me about the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我就在想  怎么会发生这样的事情\N{\fs12}and l guess l started to think about how something like that might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.22,0:31:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人如何发现自己处于那样的环境中\N{\fs12}how someone might find themselves in that type of a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.92,0:31:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就在想那次袭击是不是真的\N{\fs12}And l guess l began to wonder if the attack was random
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是由于他生活方式造成的结果\N{\fs12}or if it was the result of a lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.20,0:31:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.78,0:31:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在想  也许你能跟我说说这件事\N{\fs12}And l guess l thought that maybe you could tell me something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.68,0:31:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  塔利克  这是法庭第三次驳回我们的上诉了\N{\fs12}l'm really sorry, Taliek, but the Third Circuit denied our appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.32,0:31:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你一定不要放弃\N{\fs12}But you can't give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.90,0:31:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经向最高法院递交了一些材料\N{\fs12}l've filed some papers with the Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他们能同意审理我们的案子\N{\fs12}Hopefully they'll agree to hear our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.52,0:31:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们是怎么做的吗\N{\fs12}Do you know how they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.12,0:31:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.40,0:31:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么杀死我\N{\fs12}How they kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.36,0:31:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,靠注射\N{\fs12}lt's an injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.86,0:31:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当毒瘾犯了的时候  他们会给我换上尿布\N{\fs12}They put me in a diaper because sometimes when the drugs hit you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.29,0:31:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会失去对全身功能的控制\N{\fs12}you lose control of your functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.94,0:31:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,塔利克\N{\fs12}Taliek.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们会把我绑起来\N{\fs12}Then they strap me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.14,0:32:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给我三针\N{\fs12}They give me three shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.36,0:32:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,第一针应该是让我睡着\N{\fs12}First one's supposed to make me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.88,0:32:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,第二针应该是不让我呼吸\N{\fs12}The second one's supposed to stop me from breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.74,0:32:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一个应该是让我的心脏停工\N{\fs12}And the last one's supposed to shut down my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,让它停止跳动\N{\fs12}stop it from pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说有的时候第一针甚至不会起效果\N{\fs12}l heard sometimes the first shot doesn't even work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.20,0:32:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就躺在那\N{\fs12}So you lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.54,0:32:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就只能躺在那\N{\fs12}You just lie there and...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想要呼吸\N{\fs12}You want to breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.02,0:32:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你动不了\N{\fs12}but you can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,之后你能感觉到你的心脏停止\N{\fs12}and you can feel your heart stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.40,0:32:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你能感觉到的\N{\fs12}You can feel it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.20,0:32:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说这是世界上最痛苦的了\N{\fs12}They say it's the worst pain in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对于看着的人来说  你就只是躺在那里\N{\fs12}To everybody watching, it looks like you're just lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.74,0:32:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你能感觉到\N{\fs12}But you can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.82,0:33:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能感觉到自己慢慢死亡\N{\fs12}You can feel yourself dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.52,0:33:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我来吗\N{\fs12}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.40,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  进来吧\N{\fs12}Yeah, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.54,0:33:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你会LSP吗\N{\fs12}Listen, are you through with that LSP?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.48,0:33:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一点点吧\N{\fs12}Just about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.98,0:33:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那你会某种形式或者东西\N{\fs12}Are you gonna have some kind of a form or something
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能实时向别人展示会议吗\N{\fs12}to show these guys in time for the meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.68,0:33:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我会\N{\fs12}Yeah, l will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.46,0:33:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们有四票  他们也有四票\N{\fs12}Well, we got four votes. They got four.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.34,0:33:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得最后就看兰德斯堡了\N{\fs12}l think it's gonna come down to Landsburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.18,0:33:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你需要就在会议室说服他\N{\fs12}l guess you're gonna have to convince him right in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.68,0:33:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.58,0:33:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  嗯  我认真的  如果他们把你投出去  我就\N{\fs12}Nicholas, um, l meant what l said. If they vote you out, l'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.32,0:33:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别  别  不要这样\N{\fs12}Please. Please, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  儿子  这就是我想的\N{\fs12}Well, that's the way l feel, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.66,0:33:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这没有人对你有意见  是我  一直都是因为我\N{\fs12}No one here has a problem with you. It's me. It's always been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是认真的\N{\fs12}No. l meant what l said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.38,0:33:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你  如果他们把我投出去了  你要留下来\N{\fs12}l'm asking you. If they vote me out, then you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:33:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,会议四点开始\N{\fs12}The meeting's at 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.06,0:34:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.10,0:34:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想跟你说谢谢\N{\fs12}l just wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.30,0:34:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道昨晚你跟凯特聊过了\N{\fs12}l know you talked to Kate last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢我\N{\fs12}Don't thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.24,0:34:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  我的意思是你本可以  - 我不会的\N{\fs12}- Well, l mean you could've-- - l wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.09,0:34:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}l knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.10,0:34:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她说你变了  我希望是真的\N{\fs12}She said you've changed. l hope that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.54,0:34:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经变回来了  凯特什么都不需要担心了\N{\fs12}l have changed. Kate's got nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.64,0:34:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  说实话  我以前更喜欢你一点\N{\fs12}Well, truth be told, l think l liked you a little better before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.56,0:34:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  呃  今天我不会改变我的投票\N{\fs12}Nick, uh, l'm not changing my vote today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\fs12}l figured that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.50,0:35:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,检查了所有当事人信息  我都提交了结案\N{\fs12}Gone over all my clients, l filed the closed cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.98,0:35:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没做完的转给了其他律师\N{\fs12}transferred the active ones to the other lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.96,0:35:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  这个是给你的缓刑官的\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, this is for your probation officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.94,0:35:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有20分钟\N{\fs12}You still have 20 minutes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  在回去的路上我需要去曼科中心  这样时间就够了\N{\fs12}Well, l'm stopping off at the Manko Centeron the way back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.70,0:35:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去送点东西\N{\fs12}l have to drop something off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.58,0:35:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  我开玩笑呢\N{\fs12}Nick, l was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.16,0:35:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得签一下这个\N{\fs12}l gotta sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.08,0:35:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  应该就这样了\N{\fs12}Well, l guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.64,0:35:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  你全做完了\N{\fs12}Congratulations. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.72,0:35:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.20,0:35:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为现在情况有改变了吗\N{\fs12}You think things are gonna be different now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.90,0:35:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都更好了  露露\N{\fs12}Things are gonna be better, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.58,0:35:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这只会让一切变得更好\N{\fs12}This is only gonna make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.12,0:35:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你的会什么时候开始\N{\fs12}What time is your meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.72,0:35:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,四点\N{\fs12}4.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.58,0:36:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs12}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.28,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,最高法院拒绝了我们的提议\N{\fs12}The Supreme Court refused to grant Cert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会管我们的案子了\N{\fs12}They won't hear our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.32,0:36:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我已经联系了赦免委员会准备听证会\N{\fs12}So, l've contacted the Board of Pardons for a hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.64,0:36:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得这样会有用吗  - 可能会  会有用的\N{\fs12}- You think that'll work? - It might. It could.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们顺其自然吧\N{\fs12}Let's just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,塔利克\N{\fs12}Taliek--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.62,0:36:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我真的是受不了了  解雇律师  再上诉\N{\fs12}Look, l can't do this anymore. Firing lawyers, filing appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.66,0:36:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这所有的事情只不过是在拖延一个我们都知道的结果\N{\fs12}Look, all these things just delay what we all know is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.03,0:36:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我晾在这  塔利克\N{\fs12}Don't walk out on me, Taliek.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.33,0:36:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不能在这种没结果的事上投希望\N{\fs12}Look, l can't get my hopes up for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.79,0:36:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我一个人努力\N{\fs12}Don't walk out on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.40,0:37:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的日子里  我没有一天不在想念我的朋友詹姆斯\N{\fs12}There isn't a day that goes by that l don't miss my friend James!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.32,0:37:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人  塔利克\N{\fs12}He was a good man, Taliek.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.40,0:37:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明  又幽默\N{\fs12}Smart. Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.82,0:37:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有一天不在你造成的痛苦里挣扎\N{\fs12}There's not a day that goes by that l don't struggle with the pain that you caused!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想说的是\N{\fs12}What l'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.04,0:37:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯的死并不需要造成比现在更多的痛苦\N{\fs12}is James' death doesn't need to cause any more pain than it already has.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.52,0:37:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以拜托\N{\fs12}So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.84,0:37:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我自己一个人努力\N{\fs12}don't walk out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.92,0:37:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.14,0:37:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.56,0:37:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你带了些东西\N{\fs12}l brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.64,0:37:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫她莉拉\N{\fs12}They're calling her Lila.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.42,0:37:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,莉拉\N{\fs12}Lila?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.56,0:37:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的孩子\N{\fs12}That's your baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.74,0:37:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,莉拉\N{\fs12}Lila.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.70,0:38:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  法林先生  如你所知\N{\fs12}Hey, Mr. Fallin, just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.52,0:38:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有强奸那个女孩\N{\fs12}l didn't rape that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.18,0:38:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你早晚会发现我没有强奸她\N{\fs12}And you gonna see that l didn't rape her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.94,0:38:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,过得怎么样  克里斯\N{\fs12}How you doing, Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.28,0:38:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好点了\N{\fs12}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.72,0:38:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,比之前好点了\N{\fs12}l'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好点了吗  - 我好点了\N{\fs12}- You doing better? - l'm better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.14,0:38:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs12}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.20,0:38:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉好点了  法林先生\N{\fs12}l'm better now, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.84,0:38:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  兄弟们  这是莉拉  是我的女儿\N{\fs12}Hey, yo. This is Lila. This is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.28,0:38:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们  这是  看\N{\fs12}Man, this is-- Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.34,0:38:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把照片还给我\N{\fs12}Give me my picture back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.98,0:38:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你为那个家伙做什么了\N{\fs12}What did you do for that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  他只是一个当事人\N{\fs12}Oh, he's just a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.80,0:38:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把照片还给我\N{\fs12}Give me the picture back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.46,0:38:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我\N{\fs12}Listen, l'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.62,0:38:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你写一个电话\N{\fs12}l'm gonna write down a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.04,0:39:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你以后任何事情  给我打电话\N{\fs12}lf you need anything, you call me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.02,0:39:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我也会保证你能有一个很好的律师的\N{\fs12}and l'll make sure you get a very good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.08,0:39:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的任何东西  法林先生\N{\fs12}l don't need anything from you, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.18,0:39:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你确定一下  这真的是凯文的孩子吗\N{\fs12}Yo, check it out. This is really Kevin's kid, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.50,0:39:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是  是他的孩子\N{\fs12}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.84,0:39:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了  这就是我的女儿\N{\fs12}l told you! This is my daughter right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你该走了\N{\fs12}lt's time for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.12,0:41:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fs12}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\fs12}l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.34,0:41:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都不重要了\N{\fs12}It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.78,0:41:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\fs12}l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.52,0:41:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问你点事情吗\N{\fs12}Can l ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.92,0:41:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你做好选择了吗\N{\fs12}Did you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.72,0:41:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  什么选择\N{\fs12}What do you mean, did l have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.86,0:41:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在这  还是离开\N{\fs12}To be here... or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.78,0:41:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你做好选择了吗\N{\fs12}Did you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.56,0:41:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.18,0:41:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
